2. Hub ready, no valid CONFIRM (= owner OK on the scan plan) → **vibage-orient**
3. CONFIRM OK → **vibage-issue-locate** (legacy install name `vibage-locate` OK)
4. NEW-CHAT / install unclear → **vibage-bootstrap** or **vibage-init** (then using-vibage)
